            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Support Page -->
    <main class="page-section" id="support">
        <div class="container" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="showPage('home')" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">← Back to Home</button>
            
            <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">How can we help you?</h2>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem;">
                <!-- Contact Information -->
                <div>
                    <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 2rem; border-radius: var(--border-radius); margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Get in Touch</h3>
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <strong>📞 Phone:</strong> +91-1234567890
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <strong>✉️ Email:</strong> support@swadeshimart.com
                        </div>
                        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                            <strong>📍 Address:</strong> 123 Market Street, New Delhi, India - 110001
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <strong>🕒 Hours:</strong> Mon-Sat: 9 AM - 9 PM, Sun: 10 AM - 6 PM
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- FAQ Section -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
                        <div style="border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: var(--border-radius);">
                            <div class="faq-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                                <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(1)" style="padding: 1rem; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--light-gray);">
                                    <span><strong>How do I track my order?</strong></span>
                                    <span id="faq-icon-1">+</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="faq-answer" id="faq-answer-1" style="padding: 1rem; display: none;">
                                    You can track your order by logging into your account and visiting the "Order History" section. You'll also receive tracking information via email and SMS.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="faq-item" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);">
                                <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(2)" style="padding: 1rem; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: var(--light-gray);">
                                    <span><strong>What is your return policy?</strong></span>
